The paper deals with range aggregation and selection problems in multidimensional data structures, which are fundamental topics in data structures and databases, hence cs.DS and cs.DB are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also presents some new extensions and applications for set maintenance problems, which are relevant to information retrieval (cs.IR), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and machine learning (cs.LG).
